!if $lang_choice=en or $lang=en
  This module at the moment contains $exototal activities about probability
  starting from a so-called paradox. In particular, the module contains:
  <ul>
  <li>A first series of activities ("A single game", "You choose first", "The computer chooses first") to propose the game: students are invited to learn the rules of the game, to explore some probability scenarios and to informally develop some strategies.
   This phase of the game is intended to stimulate students' curiosity. Furthermore, the activities "You choose first", "The computer chooses first" can also be used to collect data on which to perform statistical analyses.</li>
  <li>A series of exercises of different levels ("A:" easier, ..., "C:" more difficult) to explore some problems on probability that can emerge in some phases of the game.</li>
</ul>

  !goto tail
!endif
